<br>
First, we had waves of giants spawning at the same time in different places.  We had enough folks there to handle it the first time it happened, but as the war went on, we suffered a lot from overlapping waves.  Note, this was not a case of our not killing fast enough.<br>
<br>
Then we ran into the gating Generals and Priests of Zek.  I have never seen a mob gate in one of these wars before this.  Needless to say, we had some real problems as a result.<br>
<br>
The real nail in the coffin, though, was the spearmen.  Who started summoning people who hadn't even gotten close enough to see them, let alone aggro them.  People not involved in the raid were being summoned  when they zoned in.  Clerics were summoned for rezzing people.  People who camped to clear aggro got summoned when they logged back in.  <br>
<br>
I am actually curious as to how Verant managed to screw this up so completely. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=366694">Nayl</a>
